					<img class="hvres-variant-img lazy" data-original="/pic/kt/NMHTL0AZV_AgV8a2OGMMkw.gif" /></span></div><p class="hvres-source">Dị thể</p>		<div class="hvres-meaning"><a href="/whv/谅"><span class="hvres-variant han">&#35845;</span></a><a href="/whv/諒"><span class="hvres-variant han">&#63869;</span></a><p class="gray small" style="padding-left:10px"><a href="/fonts.php">Không hiện chữ?</a></p></div><p class="hvres-source">Một số bài thơ có sử dụng</p>		<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/C%E1%BA%A3m-ng%E1%BB%99-k%E1%BB%B3-01/poem-TsI3PXZ1tTC_w-3ufMiQpA">Cảm ngộ kỳ 01 - 感遇其一</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ngang/author-KAeplXpuQBYC4UQBLqb_RQ">Trần Tử Ngang</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/Chi%E1%BA%BFn-th%C3%A0nh-nam/poem-LP73myonfM4Nqw35Wkblxw">Chiến thành nam - 戰城南</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Trung-Qu%E1%BB%91c/author-7Jx-9zMDy2CyYi7fIk3zRA">Khuyết danh Trung Quốc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Di%E1%BB%87p-m%C3%A3-nhi-ph%C3%BA/poem-srqlqH7ka2gM2RBBIsxudQ">Diệp mã nhi phú - 葉馬兒賦</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/K%C3%BD-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-ho%C3%A0i-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-Thanh-Hi%C3%AAn-T%E1%BB%91-Nh%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-HblN2xdvYT_I8LjH-26WvQ">Ký đồng hoài đệ Thanh Hiên Tố Như tử - 寄同懷弟清軒素如子</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-%C4%90%E1%BB%81/author-YFWZ8afu7g2IoLevX1_E2Q">Nguyễn Đề</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ly-tao/poem-lRoe60dlSbBq5oc1ZRJWhQ">Ly tao - 離騷</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Huy%E1%BB%81n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/Qu%C3%A1-V%E1%BA%A1n-Ki%E1%BA%BFp/poem-ypRKj86M-tsbzHhJ_g7Ilg">Quá Vạn Kiếp - 過萬劫</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Huy%E1%BB%81n-Quang-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-ky6a-6Hq9AEiujrHK0DNTQ">Huyền Quang thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/T%E1%BA%B7ng-h%E1%BB%AFu-nh%C3%A2n/poem-39DMTk0IHWNZx8yk5k-jVg">Tặng hữu nhân - 贈友人</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Th%E1%BB%A5-H%C3%A0ng-th%C3%A0nh/poem-bq4pD4fyGqr7AAI7eHul1Q">Thụ Hàng thành - 受降城</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Ngao/poem-w_OMVHVuiVnLMUqZGoDfZg">Thượng Ngao - 上嶅</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-S%C6%B0-M%E1%BA%A1nh/author-ZuzXfGup2XR6D9EtGGYzeQ">Phạm Sư Mạnh</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/Tr%C3%ACnh-Thanh-H%C6%B0-%C4%91%E1%BB%99ng-ch%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-M_u4KlCU89191mzRbkAypA">Trình Thanh Hư động chủ kỳ 1 - 呈清虛洞主其一</a> (<a href="http://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Phi-Khanh/author-3K5mDhkNpasGeB0z-64AmA">Nguyễn Phi Khanh</a>)<br/></div>		</div>
